      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GEORDIE LAD (8) has been in the minors the last two, the latest showing strong pace early but gathered in and finished a nose second over 488m this track in 27.71. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Ready to find winning form. THINK POSITIVE (2) is struggling to break through but racing consistently, finishing in the minors four on end. Last start was checked in the run and finished third in a Grade 4/5 at Cannington (30.21). Harder here but will be in this for a long way. ASTON BRADLEY (1) out of the placings in a Grade 4/5 last time, colliding with another runner and finishing a 8 length seventh over 488m at this track. Has two wins from Box 1. Can do much better this time. INCREDIBLE HEART (7) has ability and finds the right scenario to bounce back.",
